            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-6f4a1f64-c30d-4d57-9805-a6b0f39bfa42">
                The Prime Minister
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-6f4a1f64-c30d-4d57-9805-a6b0f39bfa42" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
