    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-35e5207b-fa52-47c5-9f10-746bf4f6ed2e">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-35e5207b-fa52-47c5-9f10-746bf4f6ed2e">
                The Prime Minister
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-35e5207b-fa52-47c5-9f10-746bf4f6ed2e" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1950-11-07/debates/9eb806b4-5b25-4f1b-ab1f-bbddf2ba1ad2/NationalDefence(Security)#contribution-35e5207b-fa52-47c5-9f10-746bf4f6ed2e">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">I do not think a board is necessary, because there is the closest working between the organisations on both sides of the Atlantic.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-35e5207b-fa52-47c5-9f10-746bf4f6ed2e" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1950-11-07/debates/9eb806b4-5b25-4f1b-ab1f-bbddf2ba1ad2/NationalDefence(Security)#contribution-35e5207b-fa52-47c5-9f10-746bf4f6ed2e">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
